      "text": "I need you to fetch and return the full contents of these files from the andiekobbietks/llamacoder GitHub repo at main branch:\n\n1. https://raw.githubusercontent.com/andiekobbietks/llamacoder/main/app/%28main%29/page.tsx\n2. https://raw.githubusercontent.com/andiekobbietks/llamacoder/main/components/header.tsx\n3. https://raw.githubusercontent.com/andiekobbietks/llamacoder/main/components/code-runner.tsx\n\nFor each file, return:\n- The file path\n- A brief summary (2-3 sentences) of what this file does\n- The key exports/functions/APIs it contains\n\nDo NOT return the full file contents - just the summaries. I need to understand the purpose and key functions of each file.",
